      "expandable": false
    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.2",
          "pli": "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko kaṭuko pharuso antarāyiko anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāya. ",
          "en": "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal, bitter, and harsh. They’re an obstacle to reaching the supreme sanctuary. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.3",
          "pli": "Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: ",
          "en": "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a certain person, I understand: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.4",
          "pli": "‘na cāyamāyasmā pitupi hetu … pe … ",
          "en": "‘This venerable would not tell a deliberate lie even for the sake of their father. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.5",
          "pli": "(vitthāretabbaṃ) … ",
          "en": "(To be expanded as in SN 17.37.) "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.6",
          "pli": "bhātupi hetu … ",
          "en": "brother … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.7",
          "pli": "bhaginiyāpi hetu … ",
          "en": "sister … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.8",
          "pli": "puttassapi hetu … ",
          "en": "son … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.9",
          "pli": "dhītuyāpi hetu … ",
          "en": "daughter … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.10",
          "pli": "pajāpatiyāpi hetu sampajānamusā bhāseyyā’ti. ",
          "en": "wife.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.11",
          "pli": "Tamenaṃ passāmi aparena samayena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ sampajānamusā bhāsantaṃ. ",
          "en": "But some time later I see them tell a deliberate lie because their mind is overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.12",
          "pli": "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko kaṭuko pharuso antarāyiko anuttarassa yogakkhemassa adhigamāya. ",
          "en": "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity—bitter and harsh, an obstacle to reaching the supreme sanctuary. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.13",
          "pli": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: ",
          "en": "So you should train like this: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.14",
          "pli": "‘uppannaṃ lābhasakkārasilokaṃ pajahissāma, na ca no uppanno lābhasakkārasiloko cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassatī’ti. ",
          "en": "‘We will give up arisen possessions, honor, and popularity, and we won’t let them occupy our minds.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.15",
          "pli": "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ",
          "en": "That’s how you should train.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.16",
          "pli": "Terasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:1.17",
          "pli": "Catuttho vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:2.1",
          "pli": "Bhindi mūlaṃ duve dhammā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:2.2",
          "pli": "pakkantaṃ ratha mātari; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:2.3",
          "pli": "Pitā bhātā ca bhaginī, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:2.4",
          "pli": "putto dhītā pajāpatīti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn17.38-43:2.5",
          "pli": "Lābhasakkārasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. ",
          "en": "The Linked Discourses on possessions, honor, and popularity are complete."
        }
      ],
